makes a study of fashionable apparel The new Spring Modart models still further reveal the fact that this corset is without an equal as a figure shap ing garment It is beautifully designed to mold the figure into lines of symetry and will maintain these lines when once developed All MODART Corsets lace in front because front adjust ment means right adjustment The absence of laces in the back gives better form and wonderful smoothness in gown fitting You will be assured of being properly corseted if you select your new MODART in our corset section When you have selected the corset MODART model and have been fitted by our expert corsetierre you will feel so much better and look so much better that you will seem to have become a new woman UNFAIR LIST HAKBKK SHOPS I H Turner 1104 Hewitt Barnhart Shop Monroe BUILDING LABORERS L Starke Emit Mltersbach John Grant COFFEE"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-04-26T11:23:38.786Z", "group": ["ndnp/wa", "washington-state-library-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88085620/1921-02-18/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wa:batch_wa_american_ver02:data:sn88085620:00211107625:1921021801:0591/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=464&w=355", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wa:batch_wa_american_ver02:data:sn88085620:00211107625:1921021801:0591/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=929&w=710", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/wa/batch_wa_american_ver02/data/sn88085620/00211107625/1921021801/0591.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["snohomish", "united states", "everett", "washington"], "location_city": ["everett"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["snohomish"], "location_state": ["washington"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["